{"type": "article", "id": 42955, "title": "75美元的工作围裙，多功能、好看且酷｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-07-12T23:04:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 6976, "name": "Kutarq studio"}, {"id": 32873, "name": "OTHR"}, {"id": 42291, "name": "JÖRD"}, {"id": 42292, "name": "Koala Tools"}, {"id": 38178, "name": "Jordan Bolton"}, {"id": 42293, "name": "Elian Chali"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 132, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170712184044TsWgPCau6ZdREHhS.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>JÖRD Apron by JÖRD</h3><p>还记得那个专门为创意人士打造的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/36159.html\">工作服系列</a>吗？来自加拿大的双人设计工作室 JÖRD 同样致力于开发让人们在工作时能够更有效率且美观的防护服，这条五合一的可定制围裙是他们经历多次调整后推出的产品线。所有围裙都采用手工缝制，围裙上的可拆卸配件可以根据需要调整位置，提升工作效率。防污和防水性也是 JÖRD 主打特色，织物表面加入了名为 ULTRAPEL 的保护层，号称不会让围裙染上血渍或是油污。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1053689717/jord-the-ultimate-stains-and-liquids-repels-5-in-1\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价从 75 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184115VQIkhWz4lrKMpnAq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.659375\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184116YAN05tKHnDBIcXaO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184116tJ6EnBVSmcjUGrOC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184116rqxiPQ4AjoSMWYCs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184115ejaXblgTHsrEp7wZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><h3>Cerco Espresso Cup by Kutarq Studio</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/38225.html\">专做 3D 打印家居</a>的纽约设计品牌 <a href=\"https://www.othr.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OTHR</a> 最近和西班牙设计工作室 <a href=\"http://kutarq.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kutarq Studio</a> 合作，推出了这款名为 Cerco 的咖啡杯。咖啡杯延续了 OTHR 旗下产品简约的风格，像是耳环的把手不仅满足了实用性，从俯拍照来看，也起到了装饰效果。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.othr.com/products/cerco-espresso-cup\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 85 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184137D6nMfYrtkCsdug0E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184137laEUv52197niFAcG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184138uYRCBgteiVl3zG82.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184137dxYj39f1V45e0ouv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Ring Ruler by Koala Tools</h3><p>要画圆的时候，我们通常会使用圆规，美中不足的是，它们有时会在纸上留下洞眼，而且也没有办法快速地调整大小。为了让画圆变得更简单，美国文具设计品牌 <a href=\"http://www.koalatools.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Koala Tools</a> 推出了所见即所得的圆形尺 Ring Ruler。尺上的刻度分别是圆的直径和它的对应周长，画圆时只要将尺子上的两头扣在插槽上，就能沿着它画出完美的圆形了。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.koalatools.com/Ring-Ruler-Circular-Measuring-Tool-p/kt-02.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 11.95 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184149IHVP8fhg264L3jQ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184149jSz1AbZDE8pORvkl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184149kdoMYA45KwCpeVgP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.838095\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><h3>TV posters by Jordan Bolton</h3><p>还记得那个喜欢把电影中的细节排列出来，做成海报的英国摄影师 <a href=\"http://jordanbolton.tumblr.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jordan Bolton</a> 吗？最近，他又用同样的方式为热门电视剧制作了海报。和我们之前介绍的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/38364.html\">吉卜力海报</a>一样，Bolton 似乎一直在尝试不同的道具原料。仔细观察这些电视剧海报，你会发现里面的物品大部分都是剪纸，最下方还配有标志性的行李箱，上面印有剧集的名称。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/JordanBoltonDesign\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些海报，售价从 9.30 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184202sXT6VAw0hrZy1gM4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.420000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184203R40IQirkNhvZpGew.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.436000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184203lOXYDANHuWSQRvm7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.426667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184203z4aCyxDInJ2SQ7iB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.420000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Nook by Andrea Pallarès</h3><p>对于住在小房间的人来说，一件多功能、灵活的家具变得越来越重要。英国皇家艺术学院的 <a href=\"http://andreapallares.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Andrea Pallarès</a> 希望通过这个名为 Nook 的毕业设计项目尽可能解决人们的大部分需求。Nook 由一个白色的框架、枕头和羽绒被构成，相当于多功能的床铺：框架自带的边缘可以当作小型的办公桌使用；垫子既可以平铺，也可以通过磁吸竖起，变成一道屏风；羽绒被卷起后可以当作沙发靠背。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184328LcQCqPKJl6yDrBv7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.698765\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184329ZSsOAK0ceozb3Ihf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.698438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184329BZd7mq4PNcHWFTsh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184329QLOPEe9cY6Myghaf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184330f4w9OdvUisXjcklt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675309\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Using painting for sculptural purposes by Elian Chali</h3><p>当人们驾车驶入法国圣杰维（Saint Gervais）的一个停车场时，或许会产生自己进入异世界的错觉：原本灰白色主导的地下空间内，漆上了颜色鲜艳的几何图案，从某些角度看去，它们就像是立体雕塑一样。这个利用颜色打造的作品出自阿根廷艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.elianelian.com.ar/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Elian Chali</a> 之手，当人们进入这个空间时，原本的墙壁因为图案似乎有了一种侵略性，让观众得以重新审视自己与环境的关系。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707121842212QSMarjlb4LmxN0v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623472\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184220vW8ipdJRhLr3Hotm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184220HajM9rweVfTc8QoN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712184221oWLQ5f04ZwKF9siM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>"}